    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将针对</span><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: blue; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=923540006109319168\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》</span></a><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进行修订。现进行规则公示，公示期：2026年1月26日- 2026年2月1日，规则预计于 2026年2月2日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：违规场景新增店铺信息不一致。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增内容如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">8.1.3</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺信息不一致：指商品主图中出现的店铺名称信息，与当前商品所属店铺名称不一致的情形。</span></span></p>",
